# {{ .Name }} ({{ .Type }})

Publishes a versioned artifact for a plugin catalog entry. The `url` points to the Docker image
in the registry (format: `host/image:semver`). Cycloid asynchronously pulls and validates the
image; Terraform polls until processing succeeds or fails (up to 10 minutes, 5-second interval).

A failed version taints the resource — re-run `terraform apply` to retry. Once a version
reaches `success` status it can be installed with [`cycloid_plugin`](plugin).

